enum Cbs::Filter::Mode
 

filter mode (Cell Broadcast Message Type Mode - 3GPP TS 27.005 V4.1.0 [3.3.4])

Enumerator:
Normal  declares, that the message type lists (message identifier & data coding scheme) are accepted.
Inverted  declares, that the message type lists (message identifier & data coding scheme) are not accepted
